title: What are some good Korean and English songs to sing for the JYP audition? - Quora

response.answer_text: I have asked this before some where else and heres what I got recommended: 1) (G)I-DLE - put it straight 2) wonder - V (BTS) 3) sweet but psycho 4) love yourself 5) April fools - Jimin 6) paper heart 7) Santa tell me
